293
00:15:00,781 --> 00:15:02,581
You've been standing on you soapbox for long.

294
00:15:02,581 --> 00:15:03,881
No. I...

295
00:15:03,881 --> 00:15:05,481
I am Japanese!

296
00:15:05,481 --> 00:15:07,481
I don't care about elf or whatever it is!

297
00:15:07,481 --> 00:15:08,981
Stop it, please!

298
00:15:10,881 --> 00:15:12,281
If you say so,

299
00:15:12,281 --> 00:15:13,781
