306
00:15:36,081 --> 00:15:38,181
I can't cooperate with you people anymore!

307
00:15:38,181 --> 00:15:39,581
I'm gonna go home.

308
00:15:39,581 --> 00:15:41,481
Wait, Mr. Kojima.

309
00:15:41,481 --> 00:15:42,581
I saw it.

310
00:15:46,681 --> 00:15:49,181
I saw Mr. Kojima

311
00:15:49,181 --> 00:15:51,581
