00:16:07,681 --> 00:16:09,381
You saw him, right?

320
00:16:09,381 --> 00:16:11,681
Conan?

321
00:16:13,881 --> 00:16:15,781
You rascal!

322
00:16:15,781 --> 00:16:17,581
Say that again, I'm gonna...

