324
00:16:20,181 --> 00:16:21,281
Yeah!

325
00:16:21,281 --> 00:16:23,281
Hey, why do you trust him?

326
00:16:23,281 --> 00:16:25,681
I don't understand. Don't you see it's strange?

327
00:16:25,681 --> 00:16:28,781
