364
00:18:02,281 --> 00:18:05,481
But you said you know that he found Mr. Rutger first?

365
00:18:07,181 --> 00:18:09,481
I told you, I saw it!

366
00:18:09,481 --> 00:18:11,881
I saw this kid kicking the ball alone.

367
00:18:11,881 --> 00:18:13,881
So you know,

368
00:18:13,881 --> 00:18:15,281
