370
00:18:17,681 --> 00:18:19,381
Right, Inspector?

371
00:18:19,381 --> 00:18:21,881
Sure, that's true.

372
00:18:21,881 --> 00:18:25,281
But how did you know that Genta found Mr. Rutger?

